Very few serials will make you feel like watching a movie. This one exceeds that expectations and delivers very interestingly true character. Holmes make you pounding for more reasons to believe his sayings. People call him a freak, which is totally accepted taking into account what he does to all of them. Imagine someone telling you were you went, what you did, how you did and n+ reasons to freak you out? you call 'em freak right? that's exactly what Holmes does here. Watch this serial if your brain rots without solving mysteries. Though this does not closely resemble the old fashioned book, but it sure does promises to pack a whole lot of actions to keep you at your tips!!! enjoy the show ladies and gentlemen..